<![CDATA[<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">Hi {{ contact.firstname }},</p><p><br></p><p>Hope your week is going great! I gave you a call yesterday and wanted to follow up on the previous email. In order for NWMLS to approve your IDX request form they require you to be registered with the US Copyright Office, once registered I can add the DMCA Notice to the footer of your site.</p><p><br></p><p>Please follow the steps below to register with the US Copyright Office:</p><p><br></p><p>1. Click<a href="https://dmca.copyright.gov/osp/login.html" class="ProsemirrorEditor-link"> </a><u><a href="https://dmca.copyright.gov/osp/login.html">HERE</a></u> to go to the US Copyright Office website.</p><p>2. Click on "Register Here" and create an account. You will receive a confirmation email.</p><p>3. Verify your account by clicking on the link in the email. Sign in to your account.</p><p>4. Click on "Add Service Provider."</p><p>5. You are the Service Provider and Designated Agent.</p><p>6. Process payment and receive email confirmation.</p><p>7. Confirm and search that you are listed on the <a href="https://dmca.copyright.gov/osp/search.html?key=&amp;action=search">DMCA Designated Agent Directory.</a></p><p><br></p><p>Additionally if you could provide your broker of record information below. Once the DMCA Notice is on the footer of your site, the brokerage logo on the top of your site and we have the brokers information we can draft the IDX request form via MLS Grid.</p><p><br></p><p>Brokerage: {{ contact.brokerage }}​</p><p>Broker of Record's Name:</p><p>Broker of Record's Email:</p><p>Domain name: {{ contact.hs_email_domain }}​</p><p><br></p><p>Let me know if you have any questions, I am happy to help!</p><p><br></p><p>Best Regards,</p><p><br></p>]]></td>
</tr>
